name: Rabbot - Arm
description:
Precisely milled arms capable of achieving incredible speeds at a surprising accuracy!

Elegant streamlined curves set Rabbot apart from Contabots specializing on physical labor. What Rabbot looses in protection is gained in speed and precision. All those years dancing and performing finally pay off
